    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I've taken such good care of her\u2014she's in pristine, showroom condition and honestly looks like she just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh new-car smell. I'm only letting her go because I'm downsizing, so my loss is definitely your gain. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to fall in love!",
