    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp gates, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Every VIN tag is present, the bushings are compliant, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances. This is an unmolested, turnkey example for the serious collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
