    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the term 'mint.' This one-owner gem has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one and has never seen a rainy day. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. All glass is original and crystal clear. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history binder with every maintenance task performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership. The engine bay is meticulously detailed, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. It sits on a brand-new set of matching Michelin Pilot Sport tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
